  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299460/extras/0839a9707332fe810e56e4765febf151.webp?t=1737955515\" width=620 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the enchanting world of Knights of the Round Peg, where players embark on a musical journey alongside a brave knight through 80 captivating levels.  <br><br>Equipped with a lute and a quiver of musical notes, the knight bravely embarks on a journey, encountering peg-filled challenges along the way.<br><br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299460/extras/f813da959609c468daaae4e72486b50c.poster.avif?t=1737955515\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299460/extras/f813da959609c468daaae4e72486b50c.webm?t=1737955515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299460/extras/f813da959609c468daaae4e72486b50c.mp4?t=1737955515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players must strategically clear pegs at each level using a limited number of balls.<br><br>As players progress, they will have the opportunity to explore the beautifully hand-drawn map of the kingdom. Each level backdrop is filled with interactive elements to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299460/extras/72b9605c875aed312f9aaae2d1de7cd0.poster.avif?t=1737955515\" width=620 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299460/extras/72b9605c875aed312f9aaae2d1de7cd0.webm?t=1737955515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299460/extras/72b9605c875aed312f9aaae2d1de7cd0.mp4?t=1737955515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299460/extras/2420e7ce95a50311dc246fa83492efdc.avif?t=1737955515\" width=616 height=1150 /></span></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299460/extras/0839a9707332fe810e56e4765febf151.webp?t=1737955515\" width=620 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the enchanting world of Knights of the Round Peg, where players embark on a musical journey alongside a brave knight through 80 captivating levels.  <br><br>Equipped with a lute and a quiver of musical notes, the knight bravely embarks on a journey, encountering peg-filled challenges along the way.<br><br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299460/extras/f813da959609c468daaae4e72486b50c.poster.avif?t=1737955515\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299460/extras/f813da959609c468daaae4e72486b50c.webm?t=1737955515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299460/extras/f813da959609c468daaae4e72486b50c.mp4?t=1737955515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players must strategically clear pegs at each level using a limited number of balls.<br><br>As players progress, they will have the opportunity to explore the beautifully hand-drawn map of the kingdom. Each level backdrop is filled with interactive elements to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299460/extras/72b9605c875aed312f9aaae2d1de7cd0.poster.avif?t=1737955515\" width=620 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299460/extras/72b9605c875aed3